---
/**
 * Embeddable widget for each live calculator: /embed/<slug>/
 *
 * Every calculator is written out as an explicit tag below rather than looked up
 * from a map. Astro resolves `client:*` islands from the literal component tag in
 * the template — a variable (`<Calculator client:load />`), a dynamic import() or
 * import.meta.glob all fail with NoMatchingImport at build time. Only the matching
 * branch renders, so a page still ships just its own calculator's JS.
 *
 * WIRED_SLUGS guards against drift: if a live calculator is missing here the build
 * fails, rather than the widget silently 404ing.
 *
 * Generated shape — when adding a calculator, add its import, its slug to
 * WIRED_SLUGS, and its tag.
 */
